{
  "video_id": "awADEuv5vWY",
  "title": "How we can use light to see deep inside our bodies and brains | Mary Lou Jepsen",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12722.0,
      "end_time": 14609.0,
      "text": "People don&#39;t realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14633.0,
      "end_time": 18791.0,
      "text": "that red light and benign near-infrared light"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18816.0,
      "end_time": 22173.0,
      "text": "go right through your hand, just like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23157.0,
      "end_time": 28343.0,
      "text": "This fact could enable better, faster and cheaper health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28696.0,
      "end_time": 31601.0,
      "text": "Our translucence is key here."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32930.0,
      "end_time": 35955.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show you how we use this key and a couple of other keys"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35979.0,
      "end_time": 38711.0,
      "text": "to see deep inside our bodies and brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 40430.0,
      "end_time": 41558.0,
      "text": "OK, so first up ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42868.0,
      "end_time": 46299.0,
      "text": "You see this laser pointer and the spot it makes on my hand?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47624.0,
      "end_time": 49510.0,
      "text": "The light goes right through my hand --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49534.0,
      "end_time": 51601.0,
      "text": "if we could bring the lights down, please --"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51625.0,
      "end_time": 52806.0,
      "text": "as I&#39;ve already shown."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52830.0,
      "end_time": 55583.0,
      "text": "But you can no longer see that laser spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 55608.0,
      "end_time": 57680.0,
      "text": "You see my hand glow."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 58130.0,
      "end_time": 61702.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because the light spreads out, it scatters."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62226.0,
      "end_time": 65434.0,
      "text": "I need you to understand what scattering is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65458.0,
      "end_time": 68260.0,
      "text": "so I can show you how we get rid of it"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68284.0,
      "end_time": 70720.0,
      "text": "and see deep inside our bodies and brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72419.0,
      "end_time": 74910.0,
      "text": "So, I&#39;ve got a piece of chicken back here."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 75683.0,
      "end_time": 77690.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 77930.0,
      "end_time": 78243.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s raw."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 80850.0,
      "end_time": 81702.0,
      "text": "Putting on some gloves."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81727.0,
      "end_time": 86270.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s got the same optical properties as human flesh."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 89204.0,
      "end_time": 93735.0,
      "text": "So, here&#39;s the chicken ... putting it on the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 94744.0,
      "end_time": 96900.0,
      "text": "Can you see, the light goes right through?"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98731.0,
      "end_time": 101464.0,
      "text": "I also implanted a tumor in that chicken."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102215.0,
      "end_time": 103395.0,
      "text": "Can you see it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103419.0,
      "end_time": 104747.0,
      "text": "Audience: Yes."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104771.0,
      "end_time": 109443.0,
      "text": "Mary Lou Jepsen: So this means, using red light and infrared light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109467.0,
      "end_time": 111923.0,
      "text": "we can see tumors in human flesh."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113117.0,
      "end_time": 114450.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a catch."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 115534.0,
      "end_time": 117828.0,
      "text": "When I throw another piece of chicken on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119137.0,
      "end_time": 120924.0,
      "text": "the light still goes through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 122500.0,
      "end_time": 124450.0,
      "text": "but you can no longer see the tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 125188.0,
      "end_time": 127807.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s because the light scatters."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 128633.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130917.00000000001,
      "text": "So we have to do something about the scatter"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130941.0,
      "end_time": 132541.0,
      "text": "so we can see the tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 134550.0,
      "end_time": 136188.0,
      "text": "We have to de-scatter the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 137245.0,
      "end_time": 138395.0,
      "text": "So ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 139785.0,
      "end_time": 142633.0,
      "text": "A technology I spent the early part of my career on"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142657.0,
      "end_time": 144125.0,
      "text": "enables de-scattering."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144720.0,
      "end_time": 146253.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called holography."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 146728.0,
      "end_time": 149664.0,
      "text": "And it won the Nobel Prize in physics in the 70s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149688.0,
      "end_time": 153720.0,
      "text": "because of the fantastic things it enables you to do with light."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 154879.0,
      "end_time": 156146.0,
      "text": "This is a hologram."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 156934.0,
      "end_time": 161505.0,
      "text": "It captures all of the light, all of the rays, all of the photons"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 161529.0,
      "end_time": 166390.0,
      "text": "at all of the positions and all of the angles, simultaneously."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 167173.0,
      "end_time": 168323.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168831.0,
      "end_time": 171462.0,
      "text": "To see what we can do with holography ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 173220.0,
      "end_time": 174498.0,
      "text": "You see these marbles?"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 174522.0,
      "end_time": 177231.0,
      "text": "Look at these marbles bouncing off of the barriers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 177688.0,
      "end_time": 181417.0,
      "text": "as an analogy to light being scattered by our bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182323.0,
      "end_time": 186339.0,
      "text": "As the marbles get to the bottom of the scattering maze,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186363.0,
      "end_time": 190430.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re chaotic, they&#39;re scattering and bouncing everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191460.0,
      "end_time": 195251.0,
      "text": "If we record a hologram at the bottom inside of the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 195276.0,
      "end_time": 201815.0,
      "text": "we can record the position and angle of each marble exiting the maze."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 202339.0,
      "end_time": 204853.0,
      "text": "And then we can bring in marbles from below"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 206610.0,
      "end_time": 212209.0,
      "text": "and have the hologram direct each marble to exactly the right position and angle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 212233.0,
      "end_time": 217495.0,
      "text": "such as they emerge in a line at the top of the scatter matrix."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219162.0,
      "end_time": 221780.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re going to do that with this."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 221732.0,
      "end_time": 226140.0,
      "text": "This is optically similar to human brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 226787.0,
      "end_time": 229477.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to switch to green light now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 229501.0,
      "end_time": 233259.0,
      "text": "because green light is brighter to your eyes than red or infrared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 233283.0,
      "end_time": 235243.0,
      "text": "and I really need you to see this."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 235665.0,
      "end_time": 240489.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;re going to put a hologram in front of this brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 240514.0,
      "end_time": 243180.0,
      "text": "and make a stream of light come out of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 244831.0,
      "end_time": 247760.0,
      "text": "Seems impossible but it isn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 247784.0,
      "end_time": 249989.0,
      "text": "This is the setup you&#39;re going to see."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 250140.0,
      "end_time": 251164.0,
      "text": "Green light."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 252514.0,
      "end_time": 255379.0,
      "text": "Hologram here, green light going in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 255403.0,
      "end_time": 256553.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s our brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 258458.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262849.0,
      "text": "And a stream of light comes out of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 262873.0,
      "end_time": 267603.0,
      "text": "We just made a brain lase of densely scattering tissue."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 267627.0,
      "end_time": 270897.0,
      "text": "Seems impossible, no one&#39;s done this before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 270921.0,
      "end_time": 273661.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re the first public audience to ever see this."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 273685.0,
      "end_time": 278471.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 278495.0,
      "end_time": 282162.0,
      "text": "What this means is that we can focus deep into tissue."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 282805.0,
      "end_time": 285815.0,
      "text": "Our translucency is the first key."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 285839.0,
      "end_time": 289870.0,
      "text": "Holography enabling de-scattering is the second key"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 289894.0,
      "end_time": 293761.0,
      "text": "to enable us to see deep inside of our bodies and brains."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 294981.0,
      "end_time": 296647.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re probably thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 297118.0,
      "end_time": 300127.0,
      "text": "\"Sounds good, but what about skull and bones?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 300151.0,
      "end_time": 304221.0,
      "text": "How are you going to see through the brain without seeing through bone?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 304245.0,
      "end_time": 306533.0,
      "text": "Well, this is real human skull."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 307188.0,
      "end_time": 310323.0,
      "text": "We ordered it at skullsunlimited.com."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 310347.0,
      "end_time": 312920.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 312117.0,
      "end_time": 313355.0,
      "text": "No kidding."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 313379.0,
      "end_time": 318103.0,
      "text": "But we treat this skull with great respect at our lab and here at TED."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 318127.0,
      "end_time": 319723.0,
      "text": "And as you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 320770.0,
      "end_time": 322760.0,
      "text": "the red light goes right through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 323912.0,
      "end_time": 325447.0,
      "text": "Goes through our bones."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 325471.0,
      "end_time": 330489.0,
      "text": "So we can go through skull and bones and flesh with just red light."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 331268.0,
      "end_time": 334996.0,
      "text": "Gamma rays and X-rays do that, too, but they cause tumors."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 335637.0,
      "end_time": 338713.0,
      "text": "Red light is all around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 339137.0,
      "end_time": 342410.0,
      "text": "So, using that, I&#39;m going to come back here"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 342650.0,
      "end_time": 345468.0,
      "text": "and show you something more useful than making a brain lase."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 346229.0,
      "end_time": 350183.0,
      "text": "We challenged ourselves to see how fine we could focus through brain tissue."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 350967.0,
      "end_time": 353680.0,
      "text": "Focusing through this brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 353930.0,
      "end_time": 357667.0,
      "text": "it was such a fine focus, we put a bare camera die in front of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 358288.0,
      "end_time": 360880.0,
      "text": "And the bare camera die ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 363454.0,
      "end_time": 365810.0,
      "text": "Could you turn down the spotlight?"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 365105.0,
      "end_time": 366255.0,
      "text": "OK, there it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 367117.0,
      "end_time": 368276.0,
      "text": "Do you see that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 368300.0,
      "end_time": 372576.0,
      "text": "Each pixel is two-thousandths of a millimeter wide."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 373673.0,
      "end_time": 375770.0,
      "text": "Two microns."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 375101.0,
      "end_time": 378490.0,
      "text": "That means that spot focus -- full width half max --"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 378514.0,
      "end_time": 380304.0,
      "text": "is six to eight microns."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 381600.0,
      "end_time": 383654.0,
      "text": "To give you an idea of what that means:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 384442.0,
      "end_time": 388444.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the diameter of the smallest neuron in the human brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 389300.0,
      "end_time": 393750.0,
      "text": "So that means we can focus through skull and brain to a neuron."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 394104.0,
      "end_time": 397738.0,
      "text": "No one has seen this before, we&#39;re doing this for the first time here."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 398207.0,
      "end_time": 399796.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not impossible."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 399820.0,
      "end_time": 401762.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 401786.0,
      "end_time": 404768.0,
      "text": "We made it work with our system, so we&#39;ve made a breakthrough."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 404792.0,
      "end_time": 406592.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 406617.0,
      "end_time": 409569.0,
      "text": "Just to give an idea -- like, that&#39;s not just 50 marbles."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 409593.0,
      "end_time": 412490.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s billions, trillion of photons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 412514.0,
      "end_time": 415910.0,
      "text": "all falling in line as directed by the hologram,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 415934.0,
      "end_time": 421500.0,
      "text": "to ricochet through densely scattering brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 421290.0,
      "end_time": 423966.0,
      "text": "and emerge as a focus."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 423990.0,
      "end_time": 425998.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 426220.0,
      "end_time": 427299.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re excited about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 427728.0,
      "end_time": 429760.0,
      "text": "This is an MRI machine."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 429784.0,
      "end_time": 431945.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a few million dollars, it fills a room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 431970.0,
      "end_time": 434156.0,
      "text": "many people have probably been in one."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 434180.0,
      "end_time": 435720.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spent a lot of time in one."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 435744.0,
      "end_time": 438141.0,
      "text": "It has a focus of about a millimeter --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 438165.0,
      "end_time": 440998.0,
      "text": "kind of chunky, compared to what I just showed you."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 441220.0,
      "end_time": 446680.0,
      "text": "A system based on our technology could enable dramatically lower cost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 446704.0,
      "end_time": 448519.0,
      "text": "higher resolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 448543.0,
      "end_time": 451360.0,
      "text": "and smaller medical imaging."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 451680.0,
      "end_time": 453549.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s what we&#39;ve started to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 454180.0,
      "end_time": 458408.0,
      "text": "My team and I have built a rig, a lab rig"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 458432.0,
      "end_time": 460288.0,
      "text": "to scan out tissue."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 460797.0,
      "end_time": 462463.0,
      "text": "And here it is in action."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 462932.0,
      "end_time": 465740.0,
      "text": "We wanted to see how good we could do."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 466535.0,
      "end_time": 468596.0,
      "text": "We&#39;ve built this over the last year."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 469626.0,
      "end_time": 471150.0,
      "text": "And the result is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 471814.0,
      "end_time": 476151.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re able to find tumors"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 476175.0,
      "end_time": 477345.0,
      "text": "in this sample --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 477369.0,
      "end_time": 480510.0,
      "text": "70 millimeters deep, the light going in here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 480534.0,
      "end_time": 482748.0,
      "text": "half a millimeter resolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 482772.0,
      "end_time": 485600.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the tumor it found."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 485526.0,
      "end_time": 487987.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re probably looking at this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 488110.0,
      "end_time": 493200.0,
      "text": "like, \"Sounds good, but that&#39;s kind of a big system."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 493260.0,
      "end_time": 497577.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s smaller than a honking-big MRI machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 497601.0,
      "end_time": 498951.0,
      "text": "monster MRI machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 498975.0,
      "end_time": 501140.0,
      "text": "but can you do something to shrink it down?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 502380.0,
      "end_time": 503822.0,
      "text": "And the answer is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 503846.0,
      "end_time": 505160.0,
      "text": "of course."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 505400.0,
      "end_time": 508660.0,
      "text": "We can replace each big element in that system"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 508684.0,
      "end_time": 510279.0,
      "text": "with a smaller component --"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 510303.0,
      "end_time": 512200.0,
      "text": "a little integrated circuit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 512224.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516363.00000000006,
      "text": "a display chip the size of a child&#39;s fingernail."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 517451.0,
      "end_time": 519600.0,
      "text": "A bit about my background:"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 519299.99999999994,
      "end_time": 525265.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve spent the last two decades inventing, prototype-developing"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 525289.0,
      "end_time": 530247.0,
      "text": "and then shipping billions of dollars of consumer electronics --"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 530272.0,
      "end_time": 532577.0,
      "text": "with full custom chips --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 532601.0,
      "end_time": 535337.0,
      "text": "on the hairy edge of optical physics."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 535919.0,
      "end_time": 540601.0,
      "text": "So my team and I built the big lab rig"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 540625.0,
      "end_time": 545367.0,
      "text": "to perfect our architecture and test the corner cases"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 545849.0,
      "end_time": 548400.0,
      "text": "and really fine-tune our chip designs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 548640.0,
      "end_time": 551713.0,
      "text": "before spending the millions of dollars to fabricate each chip."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 552318.0,
      "end_time": 556990.0,
      "text": "Our new chip inventions slim down the system, speed it up"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 557140.0,
      "end_time": 561970.0,
      "text": "and enable rapid scanning and de-scattering of light"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 561121.0,
      "end_time": 562988.0,
      "text": "to see deep into our bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 563498.0,
      "end_time": 569230.0,
      "text": "This is the third key to enable better, faster and cheaper health care."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 573577.0,
      "end_time": 580282.0,
      "text": "This is a mock-up of something that can replace the functionality"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 580306.0,
      "end_time": 583276.0,
      "text": "of a multimillion-dollar MRI machine"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 583300.0,
      "end_time": 585990.0,
      "text": "into a consumer electronics price point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 586140.0,
      "end_time": 591347.0,
      "text": "that you could wear as a bandage, line a ski hat, put inside a pillow."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 591882.0,
      "end_time": 593554.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s what we&#39;re building."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 593578.0,
      "end_time": 594747.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 594771.0,
      "end_time": 596500.0,
      "text": "Oh, thanks!"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 596740.0,
      "end_time": 599490.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 599730.0,
      "end_time": 601212.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;re probably thinking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 601236.0,
      "end_time": 604690.0,
      "text": "\"I get the light going through our bodies."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 604911.0,
      "end_time": 607844.0,
      "text": "I even get the holography de-scattering the light."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 608656.0,
      "end_time": 611522.0,
      "text": "But how do we use these new chip inventions, exactly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 611547.0,
      "end_time": 612802.0,
      "text": "to do the scanning?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 613903.0,
      "end_time": 615969.0,
      "text": "Well, we have a sound approach."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 616411.0,
      "end_time": 618276.0,
      "text": "No, literally -- we use sound."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 618949.0,
      "end_time": 623490.0,
      "text": "Here, these three discs represent the integrated circuits"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 623730.0,
      "end_time": 624538.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;ve designed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 624562.0,
      "end_time": 629409.0,
      "text": "that massively reduce the size of our current bulky system."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 630157.0,
      "end_time": 633577.0,
      "text": "One of the spots, one of the chips, emits a sonic ping,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 634369.0,
      "end_time": 636230.0,
      "text": "and it focuses down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 636696.0,
      "end_time": 638777.0,
      "text": "and then we turn red light on."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 639347.0,
      "end_time": 642742.0,
      "text": "And the red light that goes through that sonic spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 642767.0,
      "end_time": 645127.0,
      "text": "changes color slightly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 645680.0,
      "end_time": 648685.0,
      "text": "much like the pitch of the police car siren changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 648709.0,
      "end_time": 650175.0,
      "text": "as it speeds past you."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 652420.0,
      "end_time": 653283.0,
      "text": "So."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 653307.0,
      "end_time": 656608.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s this other thing about holography I haven&#39;t told you yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 656632.0,
      "end_time": 657940.0,
      "text": "that you need to know."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 658427.0,
      "end_time": 663196.0,
      "text": "Only two beams of exactly the same color can make a hologram."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 663800.0,
      "end_time": 669156.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s the orange light that&#39;s coming off of the sonic spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 669180.0,
      "end_time": 671363.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s changed color slightly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 671387.0,
      "end_time": 675360.0,
      "text": "and we create a glowing disc of orange light"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 675600.0,
      "end_time": 676679.0,
      "text": "underneath a neighboring chip"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 677212.0,
      "end_time": 680839.0,
      "text": "and then record a hologram on the camera chip."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 681362.0,
      "end_time": 682577.0,
      "text": "Like so."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 682601.0,
      "end_time": 687934.0,
      "text": "From that hologram, we can extract information just about that sonic spot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 687958.0,
      "end_time": 690891.0,
      "text": "because we filter out all of the red light."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 692370.0,
      "end_time": 695964.0,
      "text": "Then, we can optionally focus the light back down into the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 695988.0,
      "end_time": 699171.0,
      "text": "to stimulate a neuron or part of the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 699195.0,
      "end_time": 704299.0,
      "text": "And then we move on to shift the sonic focus to another spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 704323.0,
      "end_time": 708283.0,
      "text": "And that way, spot by spot, we scan out the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 709309.0,
      "end_time": 711952.0,
      "text": "Our chips decode holograms"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 711976.0,
      "end_time": 717740.0,
      "text": "a bit like Rosalind Franklin decoded this iconic image of X-ray diffraction"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 717764.0,
      "end_time": 720875.0,
      "text": "to reveal the structure of DNA for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 721379.0,
      "end_time": 724571.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re doing that electronically with our chips,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 724595.0,
      "end_time": 728332.0,
      "text": "recording the image and decoding the information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 728356.0,
      "end_time": 730184.0,
      "text": "in a millionth of a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 730612.0,
      "end_time": 732286.0,
      "text": "We scan fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 733625.0,
      "end_time": 736958.0,
      "text": "Our system may be extraordinary at finding blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 737534.0,
      "end_time": 741415.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s because blood absorbs red light and infrared light."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 741439.0,
      "end_time": 743200.0,
      "text": "Blood is red."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 743995.0,
      "end_time": 745383.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a beaker of blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 745407.0,
      "end_time": 746874.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to show you."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 747704.0,
      "end_time": 750771.0,
      "text": "And here&#39;s our laser, going right through it."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 751180.0,
      "end_time": 754108.0,
      "text": "It really is a laser, you can see it on the -- there it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 754133.0,
      "end_time": 758740.0,
      "text": "In comparison to my pound of flesh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 758980.0,
      "end_time": 760526.0,
      "text": "where you can see the light goes everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 761415.0,
      "end_time": 763482.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s see that again, blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 764303.0,
      "end_time": 767600.0,
      "text": "This is really key: blood absorbs light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 767989.0,
      "end_time": 770195.0,
      "text": "flesh scatters light."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 771133.0,
      "end_time": 772521.0,
      "text": "This is significant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 772545.0,
      "end_time": 776410.0,
      "text": "because every tumor bigger than a cubic millimeter or two"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 776434.0,
      "end_time": 780213.0,
      "text": "has five times the amount of blood as normal flesh."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 781690.0,
      "end_time": 785690.0,
      "text": "So with our system, you can imagine detecting cancers early,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 785715.0,
      "end_time": 787855.0,
      "text": "when intervention is easy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 787879.0,
      "end_time": 791812.0,
      "text": "or tracking the size of your tumor as it grows or shrinks."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 792338.0,
      "end_time": 797473.0,
      "text": "Our system also should be extraordinary at finding out where blood isn&#39;t,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 797498.0,
      "end_time": 799220.0,
      "text": "like a clogged artery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 799244.0,
      "end_time": 801245.0,
      "text": "or the color change in blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 801269.0,
      "end_time": 804857.0,
      "text": "as it carries oxygen versus not carrying oxygen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 804881.0,
      "end_time": 807680.0,
      "text": "which is a way to measure neural activity."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 808872.0,
      "end_time": 813506.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a saying that \"sunlight\" is the best disinfectant."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 813530.0,
      "end_time": 815410.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s literally true."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 815563.0,
      "end_time": 821725.0,
      "text": "Researchers are killing pneumonia in lungs by shining light deep inside of lungs."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 821749.0,
      "end_time": 825300.0,
      "text": "Our system could enable this noninvasively."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 825932.0,
      "end_time": 830211.0,
      "text": "Let me give you three more examples of what this technology can do."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 830592.0,
      "end_time": 831981.0,
      "text": "One: stroke."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 832601.0,
      "end_time": 834868.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s two major kinds of stroke:"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 834892.0,
      "end_time": 837440.0,
      "text": "the one caused by clogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 837680.0,
      "end_time": 839290.0,
      "text": "and another caused by rupture."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 839530.0,
      "end_time": 843151.0,
      "text": "If you can determine the type of stroke within an hour or two,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 843175.0,
      "end_time": 847882.0,
      "text": "you can give medication to massively reduce the damage to the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 848358.0,
      "end_time": 849810.0,
      "text": "Get the drug wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 850675.0,
      "end_time": 852160.0,
      "text": "and the patient dies."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 852752.0,
      "end_time": 857479.0,
      "text": "Today, that means access to an MRI scanner within an hour or two of a stroke."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 858306.0,
      "end_time": 862577.0,
      "text": "Tomorrow, with compact, portable, inexpensive imaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 862601.0,
      "end_time": 866431.0,
      "text": "every ambulance and every clinic can decode the type of stroke"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 866455.0,
      "end_time": 868738.0,
      "text": "and get the right therapy on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 870396.0,
      "end_time": 874416.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 874441.0,
      "end_time": 875591.0,
      "text": "Thanks."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 876155.0,
      "end_time": 877305.0,
      "text": "Two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 878850.0,
      "end_time": 882681.0,
      "text": "two-thirds of humanity lacks access to medical imaging."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 883394.0,
      "end_time": 888418.0,
      "text": "Compact, portable, inexpensive medical imaging can save countless lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 889347.0,
      "end_time": 890901.0,
      "text": "And three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 890926.0,
      "end_time": 892988.0,
      "text": "brain-computer communication."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 893529.0,
      "end_time": 897877.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve shown here onstage our system focusing through skull and brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 897901.0,
      "end_time": 900631.0,
      "text": "to the diameter of the smallest neuron."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 901187.0,
      "end_time": 905474.0,
      "text": "Using light and sound, you can activate or inhibit neurons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 905498.0,
      "end_time": 908990.0,
      "text": "and simultaneously, we can match spec by spec"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 909140.0,
      "end_time": 911720.0,
      "text": "the resolution of an fMRI scanner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 911744.0,
      "end_time": 914252.0,
      "text": "which measures oxygen use in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 914276.0,
      "end_time": 917617.0,
      "text": "We do that by looking at the color change in the blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 917641.0,
      "end_time": 919973.0,
      "text": "rather than using a two-ton magnet."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 921541.0,
      "end_time": 927693.0,
      "text": "So you can imagine that with fMRI scanners today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 928617.0,
      "end_time": 933174.0,
      "text": "we can decode the imagined words, images and dreams of those being scanned."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 933665.0,
      "end_time": 936982.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re working on a system that puts all three of these capabilities"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 937600.0,
      "end_time": 938553.0,
      "text": "into the same system --"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 938577.0,
      "end_time": 941791.0,
      "text": "neural read and write with light and sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 941815.0,
      "end_time": 945942.0,
      "text": "while simultaneously mapping oxygen use in the brain --"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 945966.0,
      "end_time": 948553.0,
      "text": "all together in a noninvasive portable"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 948577.0,
      "end_time": 951363.0,
      "text": "that can enable brain-computer communication,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 951387.0,
      "end_time": 955713.0,
      "text": "no implants, no surgery, no optional brain surgery required."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 956610.0,
      "end_time": 958141.0,
      "text": "This can do enormous good"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 958165.0,
      "end_time": 962698.0,
      "text": "for the two billion people that suffer globally with brain disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 964200.0,
      "end_time": 969155.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 969179.0,
      "end_time": 971690.0,
      "text": "People ask me how deep we can go."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 971930.0,
      "end_time": 974210.0,
      "text": "And the answer is: the whole body&#39;s in reach."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 974460.0,
      "end_time": 976820.0,
      "text": "But here&#39;s another way to look at it."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 980800.0,
      "end_time": 982204.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 982228.0,
      "end_time": 984839.0,
      "text": "My whole head just lit up, you want to see it again?"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 984864.0,
      "end_time": 986940.0,
      "text": "Audience: Yes!"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 986118.0,
      "end_time": 987535.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 988442.0,
      "end_time": 990663.0,
      "text": "MLJ: This looks scary, but it&#39;s not."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 991460.0,
      "end_time": 994290.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s truly scary is not knowing about our bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 994530.0,
      "end_time": 996450.0,
      "text": "our brains and our diseases"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 996690.0,
      "end_time": 998140.0,
      "text": "so we can effectively treat them."
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 998380.0,
      "end_time": 999696.0,
      "text": "This technology can help."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 999720.0,
      "end_time": 1000871.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1000900.0,
      "end_time": 1006353.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1006370.0,
      "end_time": 1007521.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1007550.0,
      "end_time": 1008700.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}